📍MEININGER Hotel Brussels Gare Du Midi - what a way to end the Eurotrip! 🏨✨ @meininger_hotels 

If you’re heading to @tomorrowland or just exploring Brussels, this place is a game-changer. It’s ridiculously convenient (a short stroll from the train station), super clean, and has options for everyone—whether you’re traveling solo or with your squad. 

Highlights? 
🛏️ Room Options: Private rooms for those who want their own space, dorms for the social butterflies. 
🍳 Kitchen Access: Want to whip up something cheap and quick? They’ve got you covered. 
🍔 Food & Drinks: Their bar and breakfast setup were clutch after long Tomorrowland nights. 
💁‍♀️ Friendly Help Desk: Lost? Hungry? Need a Tomorrowland shuttle? They even had a dedicated Tomorrowland assistance desk (seriously, how cool?). 

It was the perfect mix of comfort and budget-friendly vibes—a rare find these days! Couldn’t have asked for a better base to recharge, reminisce about festival moments, and plan the journey home. 

So, if you’re planning your Tomorrowland 2025 trip—or just exploring Brussels—trust me, this is the place! 🖤

Truffles still tastes exactly the same and I LOVE them for that. @trufflesbangaloreofficial fle
The vibe, the food, the feeling… all still so familiar, like nothing’s changed (in the best way possible). 🥹

We went all in - ordered my fav. butter chicken burger 🍔 jalapeño poppers, their insane taco baos, chicken steak, thick shakes and of course, desserts (yes, I know thats a lot of food, BUT it is what it is) that basically shut us up mid-bite. My mouth’s watering again just typing this. 🤤 

If you’re from Bangalore, or even just visiting - this place isn’t just a meal, it’s a full-on food memory. Already planning my next visit! 💛
.

OKAY listen - the biggest sale just dropped at the @basanti_kapdeaurkoffee’s Naraina Store in Delhi starting today, i.e. 13th June! and I kid you not… I walked in thinking I’d “just see what’s there” and walked out with outfits for literally every upcoming function! 🛍️

What I loved most? The fabrics felt luxe, the styles were fresh (finally something different from what you see everywhere!), and the prices were SO GOOD I had to double check the tags. Delhi, you KNOW how rare that is. 🥲

P.S. its always nice to support a homegrown brand. ✨
